      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Martin Fierz</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:242px;\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/martin-fierz-01463649/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/88/MartinFierz.jpg/240px-MartinFierz.jpg\" width=\"240\" height=\"240\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/8/88/MartinFierz.jpg 1.5x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:MartinFierz.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Martin Fierz <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Martin Fierz</b>,<br />\na Swiss physicist, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/FIDE_titles#FIDE_Master_(FM)\">FIDE Master</a> in chess, and computer chess and <a href=\"/Checkers\" title=\"Checkers\">checkers</a> programmer. \nMartin Fierz is professor of physics at <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fachhochschule_Nordwestschweiz\">Fachhochschule Nordwestschweiz</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Windisch\">Windisch</a> \nand CEO of <i>naneos particle solutions</i>, developing and building <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nanoparticle\">nanoparticle</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sensor\">sensors</a>. \nHe holds a Ph.D. in physics from <a href=\"/ETH_Zurich\" title=\"ETH Zurich\">ETH Zurich</a>, and was <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Postdoctoral_research\">postdoc</a> at the Cluster Research Group - Department of Physics and Astronomy,  <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Hawaii_at_Manoa\">University of Hawaii at Manoa</a>. \nMartin Fierz is author of the <a href=\"/Chess_Engine_Communication_Protocol\" title=\"Chess Engine Communication Protocol\">Chess Engine Communication Protocol</a> and <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compatible chess engine <a href=\"/Muse\" title=\"Muse\">Muse</a> \n<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, \nthe <a href=\"/Checkers\" title=\"Checkers\">Checkers</a> engine <i>Cake</i> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> \nand the Checkers <a href=\"/GUI\" title=\"GUI\">GUI</a> <i>CheckerBoard</i> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> . \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2000_..._2\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#2016_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2016 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Martin_Fierz&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Martin_Fierz&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Fierz</a> (<b>2001</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.research-collection.ethz.ch/handle/20.500.11850/144998\">Ultrafast electron dynamics in gas-suspended nanoparticles</a></i>. Ph.D. thesis, <a href=\"/ETH_Zurich\" title=\"ETH Zurich\">ETH Zurich</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Fierz</a> (<b>2001</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/0-306-47111-6_6\">Electronic Relaxation Time in Metallic Nanoparticles</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/book/10.1007/b114803\">Physics of Low Dimensional Systems</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Springer_Science%2BBusiness_Media\">Springer</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Fierz</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Murray_Cash&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Murray Cash (page does not exist)\">Murray Cash</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Ed_Gilbert&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Ed Gilbert (page does not exist)\">Ed Gilbert</a> (<b>2002</b>). <i>The 2002 World Computer-Checkers Championship</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#25_3\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 25, No. 3</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Fierz</a>, Leo Scherrer, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.iast.ch/de/wir_mitarbeiter/burtscher_heinz/\">Heinz Burtscher</a> (<b>2002</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0021850202000575\">Real-time measurement of aerosol size distributions with an electrical diffusion battery</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Journal_of_Aerosol_Science\">Journal of Aerosol Science</a>, Vol. 33, No. 7</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Fierz</a>, Ralf Kaegi, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.iast.ch/de/wir_mitarbeiter/burtscher_heinz/\">Heinz Burtscher</a> (<b>2007</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.tandfonline.com/doi/full/10.1080/02786820701253327\">Theoretical and Experimental Evaluation of a Portable Electrostatic TEM Sampler</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.tandfonline.com/toc/uast20/current\">Aerosol Science and Technology</a>, Vol. 41, No. 5</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Fierz</a>, Silke Weimer, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.iast.ch/de/wir_mitarbeiter/burtscher_heinz/\">Heinz Burtscher</a> (<b>2009</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0021850208001754?via%3Dihub\">Design and performance of an optimized electrical diffusion battery</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Journal_of_Aerosol_Science\">Journal of Aerosol Science</a>, Vol. 40, No. 2</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Martin_Fierz&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Fierz</a>, Corey Houle, Peter Steigmeier, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.iast.ch/de/wir_mitarbeiter/burtscher_heinz/\">Heinz Burtscher</a> (<b>2011</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.tandfonline.com/doi/full/10.1080/02786826.2010.516283\">Design, Calibration, and Field Performance of a Miniature Diffusion Size Classifier</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.tandfonline.com/toc/uast20/current\">Aerosol Science and Technology</a>, Vol. 45, No. 1</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Fierz</a>, Dominik Meier, Peter Steigmeier, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.iast.ch/de/wir_mitarbeiter/burtscher_heinz/\">Heinz Burtscher</a> (<b>2014</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.tandfonline.com/doi/full/10.1080/02786826.2013.875981\">Aerosol Measurement by Induced Currents</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.tandfonline.com/toc/uast20/current\">Aerosol Science and Technology</a>, Vol. 48, No. 4</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Martin_Fierz&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_..._2\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Martin_Fierz&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=130980\">singular extensions?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Fierz</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 29, 2000&#160;» <a href=\"/Singular_Extensions\" title=\"Singular Extensions\">Singular Extensions</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=178124\">muliti probcut</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Fierz</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 04, 2001&#160;» <a href=\"/ProbCut#MPC\" title=\"ProbCut\">Multi–ProbCut</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=251687\">MTD: an observation and a question</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Fierz</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 11, 2002&#160;» <a href=\"/MTD(f)\" title=\"MTD(f)\">MTD(f)</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=290629\">EGTB generation with 1 bit per position?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Fierz</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 25, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/Endgame_Tablebases\" title=\"Endgame Tablebases\">Endgame Tablebases</a>, <a href=\"/Endgame_Bitbases\" title=\"Endgame Bitbases\">Endgame Bitbases</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=330947\">table-based SEE or \"evaluation in rebel (hanging pieces)\"</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Fierz</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 27, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/Hanging_Piece\" title=\"Hanging Piece\">Hanging Piece</a>, <a href=\"/Rebel\" title=\"Rebel\">Rebel</a>, <a href=\"/Static_Exchange_Evaluation\" title=\"Static Exchange Evaluation\">Static Exchange Evaluation</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=357188\">move ordering and node count</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Fierz</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 29, 2004&#160;»<a href=\"/Move_Ordering\" title=\"Move Ordering\">Move Ordering</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=381373\">Muse!</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Fierz</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 08, 2004</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=15662\">multithreading questions</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Fierz</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 08, 2007&#160;» <a href=\"/Parallel_Search\" title=\"Parallel Search\">Parallel Search</a>, <a href=\"/Thread\" title=\"Thread\">Thread</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2016_...\">2016 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Martin_Fierz&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: 2016 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=59470\">Computer chess progress over say the last 20 years?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Fierz</a>, March 10, 2016</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=59497\">Computer chess progress over the last 20 years!</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Fierz</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 13, 2016</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=59529\">Checks in qsearch - must-have or optional?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Fierz</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 15, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Check\" title=\"Check\">Check</a>, <a href=\"/Quiescence_Search#Checks\" title=\"Quiescence Search\">Checks in Quiescence Search</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=59543\">Computer Chess Progress: Stockfish 7 vs Ruffian 1.0.5</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Fierz</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 17, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Stockfish\" title=\"Stockfish\">Stockfish</a>, <a href=\"/Ruffian\" title=\"Ruffian\">Ruffian</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=59598\">Extensions in the days of LMR?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Fierz</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 22, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Extensions\" title=\"Extensions\">Extensions</a>, <a href=\"/Late_Move_Reductions\" title=\"Late Move Reductions\">LMR</a> </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=59661\">Futile attempts at futility pruning</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Fierz</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 27, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Futility_Pruning\" title=\"Futility Pruning\">Futility Pruning</a>, <a href=\"/Reverse_Futility_Pruning\" title=\"Reverse Futility Pruning\">Reverse Futility Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=59740\">Hashing in Qsearch?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Fierz</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 03, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a>, <a href=\"/Quiescence_Search\" title=\"Quiescence Search\">Quiescence Search</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=59817\">Muse 0.95</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Fierz</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 10, 2016</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=59856\">Shifting alpha/beta on hash hit</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Fierz</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 14, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Search_Instability\" title=\"Search Instability\">Search Instability</a>, <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=59960\">Hashtable aging</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Fierz</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 25, 2016</li></ul>\n<p><b>2018</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=67235\">MCTS beginner questions</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Fierz</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 25, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Monte-Carlo_Tree_Search\" title=\"Monte-Carlo Tree Search\">Monte-Carlo Tree Search</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=67302\">MCTS with minmax backup operator?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Fierz</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 01, 2018</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=67390\">cutechess-cli?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Fierz</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 09, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Cutechess-cli\" title=\"Cutechess-cli\">Cutechess-cli</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=67490\">Is cutechess-cli's rating interval 1 sigma or 2 sigma?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Fierz</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 18, 2018</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Martin_Fierz&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.fierz.ch/\">The Homepage of Martin Fierz</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.fierz.ch/strategy.htm\">Martin's World &gt;&gt; Strategy Game Programming</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.fierz.ch/history.htm\">Martin's World &gt;&gt; A brief history of computer checkers</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.fierz.ch/chess.htm\">Martin's World &gt;&gt; Chess</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.fierz.ch/muse.htm\">Martin's World &gt;&gt; Muse</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/martin-fierz-01463649/\">Martin Fierz | LinkedIn</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://ratings.fide.com/card.phtml?event=1302132\">Fierz, Martin FIDE Chess Profile</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.chessgames.com/player/martin_fierz.html\">Chess games of Martin Fierz</a> from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.chessgames.com/index.html\">chessgames.com</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.sgzurich.ch/pages/turniere/teamcup.php\">SG Zürich - Teamcup</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Jonathan_Rosenthal\" title=\"Jonathan Rosenthal